    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new adventure. This car is a total stunner and is in truly incredible, showroom-quality shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one! You won't find a single flaw, and it drives just as smoothly as the day I got it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
