    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear, visceral power delivery. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for superior torque biasing. Mechanical integrity is paramount; this chassis has undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers, ensuring the communicative handling these cars are known for. Finished in flawless Alpine White, the exterior exhibits perfect panel gaps and zero oxidation. This is a turn-key, showroom-quality example with a fully documented maintenance log.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
