    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to obsessive maintenance and preservation. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one, never seeing rain or snow. The exterior finish is breathtaking; the paint possesses a deep, glass-like clarity with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and exclusive hand-washing. Moving inside, the cabin is in 'time-capsule' condition. The premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple with no bolster wear or creasing, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners since new, and all high-gloss trim pieces are free of scratches. Every electronic feature and button functions with factory-new precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It comes with a complete, chronological service history performed exclusively by master technicians, with all preventative maintenance completed well ahead of schedule. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the buyer seeking a showroom-quality example that looks, smells, and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line, this is the one.",
      "price": 43500.0,
