      "description": "Hey there! You have to check out this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. It\u2019s been super reliable and drives like a dream. I\u2019m looking for a smooth sale, so I\u2019ve priced it fairly for its amazing shape. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
